nodes.text: Josh Peck (born November 10, 1986) is an American voice actor who voiced Pace Freemaker in LEGO Star Wars: All-Stars.

Peck is best-known for his roles in Dan Schneider's comedy series like The Amanda Show and Drake & Josh. He has also voided Eddie in the Ice Age franchise and Casey Jones in the 2012 Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles animated series.
